(7,	2431,	1150965363,	'Reported: Super Mario World MIDIS',	'Reported Submission: <a href=\'/index.php?act=resdb&amp;param=02&amp;c=5&amp;id=482\'>Super Mario World MIDIS</a> by SUPER_MAT_GAMES<br /><br />------------------------------------------------------<br />Reported By: Jouw<br /><br />The above submission was reported for the following reason:<br /><br />These MIDIs are stolen from The Mushroom Kingdom&#39;s SMW page. Here is the link: http://www.themushroomkingdom.net/db/mid<br />i.ktn?Game=smw',	7,	1150995730,	1,	482,	'I&#39;m gonna ask on this one, that&#39;s a really good report. I&#39;m not entirely sure if we should allow things like this on the site.',	0,	0),
(8,	89,	1150998383,	'Typo and question.',	'There&#39;s a typo in the message center: &quot;Subejct&quot; instead of &quot;Subject&quot;<br /><br />And what&#39;s with the files that contain both an MMF lib and a spritesheet?',	7,	1150998588,	4,	0,	'Aight, we&#39;ll get to the typo.<br />As for the lib AND spritesheet... hmm. That&#39;s a really good question. At this point, I can&#39;t say, but I&#39;d just submit it twice: once as a sheet, once as a lib.',	0,	0),
