(11,	439,	1151014956,	'Reported: Mario Left the Cheese Out',	'Reported Submission: <a href=\'/index.php?act=resdb&amp;param=02&amp;c=2&amp;id=281\'>Mario Left the Cheese Out</a> by <br /><br />------------------------------------------------------<br />Reported By: 123James<br /><br />The above submission was reported for the following reason:<br /><br />I don&#39;t know what the problem is but after I download it and go through the instalment program I click the icon and all I get a small Error window that says &quot;File error!&quot;. I don&#39;t know if the file is courrop and someone needs to give you guys a working file of the game or what. You may want to check into this.',	7,	1151078234,	1,	281,	'When we did the thumbnails, we had to play every game to make sure they worked too. As far as we know, there was no problem with MLTCO.',	0,	0),
(12,	439,	1151014982,	'Reported: Mario Left the Cheese Out',	'Reported Submission: <a href=\'/index.php?act=resdb&amp;param=02&amp;c=2&amp;id=281\'>Mario Left the Cheese Out</a> by <br /><br />------------------------------------------------------<br />Reported By: 123James<br /><br />The above submission was reported for the following reason:<br /><br />I don&#39;t know what the problem is but after I download it and go through the instalment program I click the icon and all I get a small Error window that says &quot;File error!&quot;. I don&#39;t know if the file is courrop and someone needs to give you guys a working file of the game or what. You may want to check into this.',	7,	1151078355,	1,	281,	'For some reason there&#39;s a repeat message. o_O',	0,	0),
