(16,	2479,	1151080110,	'A Problem...',	'Yes, I have a quick &quot;bug&quot; report.<br />Sometimes when either writing a review or giving a comment, the site sometimes logs me out when submiting the review or comment, thus not allowing me to post it. Is there a way for this to be fixed?',	7,	1151086991,	4,	0,	'Never heard of anything like this. My best bet is that it&#39;s something on your computer&#39;s end, like not storing cookies.',	0,	0),
(17,	77,	1151098374,	'Reported: Bowser in Mario & Luigi\'s clothes',	'Reported Submission: <a href=\'/index.php?act=resdb&amp;param=02&amp;c=1&amp;id=4208\'>Bowser in Mario & Luigi\'s clothes</a> by TJ<br /><br />------------------------------------------------------<br />Reported By: SonicProject<br /><br />The above submission was reported for the following reason:<br /><br />&quot;We will not accept useless sprites. Even if they have decent quality, sprites can still be useless. A perfect example is a Super Saiya-jin Luigi holding a shotgun... standard Mario sprites are accepted, but not absurd edits.&quot;',	7,	1151129694,	1,	4208,	'I&#39;m not even touching this.',	0,	0),
