(32,	2668,	1151409804,	'Good job!',	'new site + me = ^_^ !!!',	13,	1151466874,	4,	0,	'',	0,	0),
(33,	77,	1151420006,	'Reported: Bowser in Mario & Luigi\'s clothes',	'Reported Submission: <a href=\'/index.php?act=resdb&amp;param=02&amp;c=1&amp;id=4208\'>Bowser in Mario & Luigi\'s clothes</a> by TJ<br /><br />------------------------------------------------------<br />Reported By: SonicProject<br /><br />The above submission was reported for the following reason:<br /><br />I don&#39;t know if it got through or not the first time I reported but this sprite is still unacceptable according to the Submission Rules.',	13,	1151465652,	1,	4208,	'We decided that since two people accepted it, it was ok enough to get on, it&#39;s obviously not as useless as you make it out to be. And one person&#39;s opinion won&#39;t change the decision. Also, you&#39;re not a mod, leave the decisions to us.',	1,	0),
(34,	77,	1151465823,	'Re: Reported: Bowser in Mario & Luigi&#39;s clothes',	'To whomever replied to my report:<br /><br />Get rid of the report system if you&#39;re going to be assy about these reports. It&#39;s your f***ing submission rules not mine.',	2,	1151467475,	4,	0,	'Stop beating this issue into the ground.  The report system was NOT intended for voicing your higher standards.  Those can be left to comments, and as it stands, your opinion isn&#39;t the majority opinion.  The reports are for thefts, physical problems with files, obscene commentry and so forth.<br /><br />The sprite was accepted by two mods - no one felt it was necessary to re-evaluate it after receiving your first &#39;report&#39; (which, by the way, couldn&#39;t be responded to because no facility existed at that time).  Your report, never the less, was looked over.<br /><br />Don&#39;t turn around and get pissy at us every time the ducks aren&#39;t lined up to your expectations.<br /><br />-- Retriever II',	1,	0),
(35,	77,	1151467845,	'Re: Re: Reported: Bowser in Mario & Luigi&#39;s clothes',	'They&#39;re not my standards. They&#39;re yours. Read your submission rules. Or did you just make them to make this site look professional?<br /><br />The only reason I got pissy was because you and whoever replied to my second report treated me like I was inferior. Stop trying to one-up me and this matter will evaporate into the air.',	2,	1151468925,	4,	0,	'Settled through a personal channel.',	0,	0),
