(40,	77,	1151869908,	'Reported: Mario and Luigi Superstar saga - Wario',	'Reported Submission: <a href=\'/index.php?act=resdb&amp;param=02&amp;c=1&amp;id=1363\'>Mario and Luigi Superstar saga - Wario</a> by turdlantic<br /><br />------------------------------------------------------<br />Reported By: SonicProject<br /><br />The above submission was reported for the following reason:<br /><br />A bitmap in a zip. Probably needs to be converted to a png. :)',	13,	1151901159,	1,	1363,	'Not an urgent matter at the moment. The reason pngs are used instead of bmps is because of their size. Since bmps zipped are substantially smaller, there isn&#39;t an immediate problem.',	1,	0),
